people.name: Chris Cassidy
people.title: Commander
people.bio: Expedition 63 Commander, Cassidy served as a member of the Navy SEALs before being selected as a NASA astronaut in 2004. He was named Chief of the Astronaut Office in 2015. Cassidy has completed six spacewalks on previous missions. This is his third spaceflight.

people.name: Anatoli Ivanishin
people.title: Flight Engineer
people.bio: After serving in the Russian Air Force, Anatoli became a cosmonaut in 2005. This is his third trip to space, having traveled to the ISS twice before. Anatoli is married and he and his wife have a son.

people.name: Ivan Vagner
people.title: Flight Engineer
people.bio: Ivan was born on July 10, 1985 in Severoonezhsk. He has a Masters Degree in Aeronautical Engineering from Baltic State Technical University. Ivan was selected as a cosmonaut in 2010. This is his first spaceflight.
